1.title: Truth is Just Another Four Letter Word
1.plot: Nikki Serenity has returned to Local Ambition after the traumatic events of last year's season and gets an unexpected visit by someone from her past.

2.title: No Room for You, Cover Girl
2.plot: Nikki Serenity breaks hearts and makes one cast member's dream of being a magazine cover model come true.

3.title: Don't Stop Dreaming, Sally
3.plot: What happens when the creator of the show asks for a photo shoot with Nikki Serenity and her rival, Chelsi?

4.title: The One Where the Cast Meets Murphy Lee
4.plot: St. Louis rap legend, Murphy Lee, stops by Local Ambition to shoot a music video for his new single.

5.title: Jamileigh Did a Bad, Bad Thing
5.plot: The cast competes in the third stage of the competition and Jamileigh carries through with Chelsi's devious plan to take Nikki Serenity's host position.

6.title: Sweet Revenge
6.plot: Chelsi's the new host and the cast participates in a local independent wrestling show that has lasting consequences for everyone.

7.title: Oops, She Did It Again
7.plot: It's the final stage of the competition and the cast is feeling the pressure - some more than others. Oh, and something really bad happens again.

8.title: Do the Right Thing
8.plot: It's the final episode of the season. We find out who will be the winner of Local Ambition 7 and if Jaclyn can survive captivity.

1.title: Meet Nikki Part 1
1.plot: All the way from Sparta, Illinois, comes Nikki. She's competing in the first season of our modeling competition reality show, "Local Ambition."

2.title: Meet Nikki Part 2
2.plot: Want more Nikki? Of course you do! Here's Sparta's own, discussing how she can't be friends with guys and find out what "night cable" is.

3.title: Meet Destiny Part 1
3.plot: Meet Destiny. The other half of the "Local Celebs", with her friend, Nikki.

4.title: Meet Destiny Part 2
4.plot: Who doesn't love sequels? Here, Destiny discusses why she isn't friends with an old friend, says a word that even we had to bleep, and talks about how she was arrested.

5.title: Meet Angela
5.plot: And here's Angela! Here, she talks about why she got interested in modeling, creepy photographers, and some weirdo's foot fetish.

6.title: Meet Sarah
6.plot: Meet Sarah. She's a gamer nerd from Jerseyville, Illinois and for someone whose shy, she sure has a lot of opinions about other girls. They say its the quiet ones you have to watch out for.

7.title: Meet Elizabeth
7.plot: Elizabeth didn't want to be alone in her introduction video, so she spent the day with someone. Learn more about Elizabeth and witness the most awkward date ever.

8.title: Meet Cassandra
8.plot: Straight out of Festus, Missouri comes Cassondra.

9.title: The Party
9.plot: All of the girls from season one meet for the first time. I'd say that everyone got along and no one was out of line, but I'd be lying. Of course there was trash talking.

10.title: Team Shoots
10.plot: Watch the girls take teamwork to all-time low! No one gets along and trash talking ensues in the first competition of season one! There's also an appearance by Shawn's sister. How will Shawn react to this?

11.title: Farewell to Gums
11.plot: The fun and games are over. The girls find out who has been eliminated after the team photo shoot round.

12.title: The Final Round
12.plot: The remaining contestants go head-to-head in the final round of Local Ambition. Each girl has had to come up with their own theme and wardrobe for this round.

13.title: And the Winner Is...
13.plot: It's down to Angela and Sarah. Find out who is named the winner of the first season of Local Ambition.

1.title: Meet the Girls Part 1
1.plot: Get to know the first half of Local Ambition: Season 2's cast.

2.title: Meet the Girls Part 2
2.plot: You've met the first five girls from the competition. Now meet the last five - Nicole, Desiree, Melody, Amanda, and Sweeney.

3.title: Christine Is a Drunk Slob
3.plot: It's the first elimination of season two and the judges decide which girls are going to be sent home.

4.title: Oh Captain, My Captain
4.plot: It's time for Round 2 - the Comic Book Round. The girls designed their own costumes and came up with their super hero (or villain) identities. The Heroes team goes head to head against the Villains to see which side gets immunity.

5.title: Good Sh*T, Me
5.plot: Round 2 is over. The girls find out what their scores were, which team won, which girl won the comic book print, and who will be going home.

6.title: Poppin' Tags
6.plot: It's the third round of Local Ambition: Season 2 and the girls are given $20 and ten minutes inside of Goodwill to come up with an outfit for their photo shoot.

7.title: The Real Nicole
7.plot: The judges address concerns over whether or not Sweeney cheated in the previous round and announce which girls will be sent home in the third elimination of the season.

8.title: The Final Round
8.plot: The final three contestants battle it out in the final round of Local Ambition: Season 2.

9.title: There Can Only Be One
9.plot: It's the season finale and the judges announce who will be the winner of Local Ambition: Season 2.

1.title: Multiple Personalities
1.plot: It's the season premiere of Local Ambition: Season Three.

2.title: Sugary Spray Tans and Mermaid Best Friends
2.plot: Get up close and personal with Danielle and Kathleen and find out which three girls will be eliminated in the first cuts of the season.

3.title: The Zombie Apocalypse
3.plot: It's the second round of Local Ambition: Season Three and the girls compete in the zombie apocalypse round. Each of them had to create looks as both zombies and as survivors.

4.title: 2nd Cut Is the Deepest
4.plot: It's the second elimination of Local Ambition: Season Three and the girls find out who is going home after the zombie apocalypse round.

5.title: Itty Bitty Teenie Weenie Yellow Polka-Dot Beekini
5.plot: It's the show's first ever swimsuit round and the remaining five girls battle it out with a sixth competitor who returns to the show.

6.title: Getting Personal
6.plot: It's the third elimination of the season and the girls find out which of them will be sent home and who will make it to the final round.

7.title: It All Started at the Lingerie Show
7.plot: It's the final round of Local Ambition: Season Three. The final six girls strut their stuff in front of our cameras in their last attempt to win favor with the judges.

8.title: Closure
8.plot: It's time to find out who was named the winner of Local Ambition: Season Three.

1.title: Season Premiere
1.plot: It's the season premiere of Always Late TV's original series, Local Ambition. This season, 13 women from St. Louis, and the surrounding area, go head-to-head in a season packed full of themed photo shoots, challenges, creativity, and drama.

2.title: Bye, Bye, Bridget
2.plot: Sarah won immunity from elimination when she won last week's challenge. While she's safe, the rest of the cast must compete in this week's photo shoot round to determine who goes home next week. The theme for this round is "Test Shoots." See what costumes and outfits the girls come up with and find out what happens to Bridget.

3.title: Everybody Hates Alicia
3.plot: Find out why everyone has a problem with Alicia in the newest episode of Local Ambition. The cast also competes in the second challenge of the season (sponsored by Bakers Shoes), with immunity awarded to the winner.

4.title: Heroes & Villains
4.plot: The cast competes in their second photo shoot round of the season - the theme is Heroes and Villains. Each cast member was assigned either a "hero" or "villain" role and had to come up with a costume and secret identity for their character for tonight's competition.

5.title: Shhh...
5.plot: The cast finds out who is going home today in the second elimination of the season. Spoiler Alert - it's not Emily. She has immunity. The girls who survive the cut will compete in a challenge sponsored by Matthew Rivers' Move in Silence clothing brand.

6.title: Making It Happen
6.plot: The cast competes in the 2nd annual swimsuit round. Watch as the cast suits up and tears it up in this scantily clad, drama filled episode.

7.title: Thrown Under the Bus
7.plot: It's elimination day once again. Since the judges did not eliminate anyone last time, more girls are going to be sent home today.

8.title: Bambi Isn't a Fairy Tale
8.plot: And then there were six. The remaining cast members compete in the fairy tale fantasy round. Each cast member was tasked to come up with their own enchanted costumes for this week's shoot.

9.title: Sucker Fish
9.plot: It's the final elimination of the season and it's time to find out which four girls will be going into the final round. Before our judges decide which two girls will be sent home, we find out what happened at a local fashion show involving our cast.

10.title: Two Sides to Every Story
10.plot: It's the final round of the season and the remaining cast members wear fashions created by Jacqueline Nicole and Honey's Child in our 3rd annual Fashion Round.

11.title: There Can Only Be One
11.plot: Just like the title suggests - there can be only one. One woman will walk away from tonight's episode the winner of Local Ambition: Season 4.

1.title: Season Premiere
1.plot: Local Ambition is back with it's fifth season and a brand new cast. Last year's winner, Sarah Galbraith, returns as this season's host. She guides the girls through several rounds of themed photo shoots and challenges.

2.title: Throwback to the Future
2.plot: Last week, you met the cast of Local Ambition 5.0 - this week, the competition begins. The cast competes in their first immunity challenge - the theme is 80's glamour shots.

3.title: Basic
3.plot: It's the first round of the season and the theme is Fall City Life. The cast must come up with their own fall fashions and model before our judges in downtown St. Louis.

4.title: The Popularity Contest
4.plot: It's the first elimination of the season and this week, we find out which two girls will be sent home by our judges. The remaining cast members will compete in our second immunity challenge - silhouettes.

5.title: There's Something About Mary (and Maggie)
5.plot: In this week's episode, the remaining cast members share their thoughts on what sci-fi is and compete in their second photo shoot round. Some performances were hits and some not so much.

6.title: Kayci's Big Day
6.plot: This week, we find out which two girls will be sent home and what's in store for the rest of the cast who survive the second elimination of the season.

7.title: HannaGate
7.plot: The cast competes in the first ever lingerie/boudoir round and revolt against a producer.

8.title: The Snitch
8.plot: The cast discovers the identity of the person who snitched to management about their insulting group chat message.

1.title: Everything Starts Here
1.plot: 11 women from St. Louis, Missouri, and the surrounding area, begin their journey through the most unique modeling competition in the country - Local Ambition.

2.title: Jessica's Fate
2.plot: Chelsi finds out about Tia's plan to get her off the show and Jessica discovers her fate.

3.title: Pretty Little Monsters
3.plot: The cast competes in their second photo shoot round - Make Your Own Monster. Chelsi's plot to get Jessica kicked off the show failed, so she stays in the competition.

4.title: Reindeer Games
4.plot: Helaina has a special message for Jessica after last week's argument; Tia has a surprise for the "Face of Local Ambition", Chelsi; and two more cast members will be sent home after this week's elimination.

5.title: Adult Friend Finder
5.plot: Mackenzie is looking for an ally after splitting with Chelsi. One of the cast members has also been kidnapped. The rest of the cast, who is still alive, compete in a pin-up photo shoot.

6.title: L'art de la tromperie
6.plot: We find out if Jessica accepted Mackenzie's offer; what comes next; and who goes home.

7.title: Persona Non Grata
7.plot: Jessica doesn't have a friend in the world. How will share fare in the competition when she's public enemy number one?

8.title: Everything Ends Here
8.plot: It's the season finale of Local Ambition and a winner will be named.
